sellerCard.oneLiner: Quality Conscious Full Stack Web Developer
sellerCard.description: Hi! I am Ammar an Experienced Software Engineer with a demonstrated history of working in Full Stack Web Development. 6+ years of experience in HTML, CSS, Angular, and ReactJs with a good base of backend development using  NodeJs, MongoDB, SQL, Python, C/C++, JavaScript, WordPress, and Shopify. I have worked with industries like eCommerce, Educational Institutes, Portfolio, Telecommunication, Pharmaceuticals, etc. I'll surely provide you a quality and on-time services. I am more than happy to have a brief discussion about your problem in a relaxed and user-friendly environment.

description.content:
About Me

Hi! I am Ammar. A Full Stack Web Developer, with 5 Years of Industrial Experience in Developing customized web applications using Angular, React, Node, and MongoDB. Worked with lots of satisfied clients mostly related to e-commerce, portfolios, multi-vendor, education, and pharmaceuticals.


》 Please reach out before placing an order to avoid any inconvenience 《

 

Technology stack:

 

Front-end:

️» Angular 10+

» Material Design - MUI

» Typescript

» ReactJS

» Bootstrap

» HTML5

» JavaScript

 

Back-end:

» Node

» Python Flask

» Express

» MongoDB

» MySQL

» PHP (Codeigniter, Laravel)

» Asp.net


My Services

» Full Stack Web Application from Scratch

» Customizing Existing Application

» Mock-ups to Front-end Development

» Responsive and Compatible Design

» Open AI Integration


Why Work with Me?

» Quality Conscious Person

» 100% happiness Guarantee (Money-Back)

» Experience in Industry

» User-Friendly and Relaxed Environment

» Worked with lots of clients (Mostly E-Commerce, Multi-vendor, and SAAS)


Note

» I will not create a logo for the website.

» I will not provide Domain and Hosting (but I can assist you in purchasing one).

» I will not provide graphical & textual content

questionsAndAnswers.question: What requirements I have to provide?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: You have to provide clear requirements including main functionalities for the website. Provide Wireframes or sketch if you can.

questionsAndAnswers.question: How long are your quotes valid for?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Our quotes are valid for a period of 30 days from the date of issuance. To ensure the accuracy of pricing and availability, please reach out if you need to extend the validity of your quote beyond this timeframe.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What types of projects have you worked on?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: My portfolio covers a wide range of projects, including e-commerce platforms, school management systems, internal management tools, review systems, health portals, AI websites, procurement systems, and transportation platforms.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Why do i need to reach you before placing an order?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: It's essential to reach out before placing an order so we can thoroughly discuss your requirements, understand your business goals, and ensure the project scope is well-defined. This approach ensures a smoother process and a product that truly meets your needs.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide any support after order completion?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, my main goal is to develop your business, not just your website. I provide free support for up to 2 weeks after project completion, which includes bug fixing and issue resolution. I’m committed to ensuring your business thrives even after the delivery of the project.

questionsAndAnswers.question: How do you charge for your services?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Depending on the project's requirements, I offer both milestone-based pricing and hourly-based models. I recommend choosing the model that best suits your budget and project needs.
